data.description: Contract failed because of financing, home is back on the market.  Pristine home in Lakeland that gives you, your boat, family access to beautiful Garner lake.  New interior paint, newly painted kit cabinets, beautiful hardwood floors, lg luxury primary bath w/ two walk in closets, inground pool with new liner, arbor, covered patio, updated pool equipment, fenced yard.
